---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const jsonLd = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Product",
  "name": "Sharples P-3400 Decanter Centrifuge",
  "description": "Sharples P-3400 decanter centrifuge — specifications, applications and rebuild services from Dolphin Centrifuge.",
  "brand": { "@type": "Brand", "name": "Dolphin Centrifuge" },
  "manufacturer": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "Dolphin Centrifuge", "url": "https://dolphincentrifuge.com" },
  "url": "https://dolphincentrifuge.com/sharples-p-3400-decanter/",
};
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Sharples P-3400 Decanter Centrifuge"
  description="Sharples P-3400 horizontal decanter centrifuge — high-volume rebuild, parts and repair from Dolphin Centrifuge. Greater capacity than P-3000 for heavy sludge applications."
  canonicalUrl="https://dolphincentrifuge.com/sharples-p-3400-decanter/"
  breadcrumbs={[{label: 'Products', href: '/decanter-centrifuge/'}, {label: 'Sharples P-3400'}]}
  jsonLd={jsonLd}
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-navy text-white">
    <div class="container-dolphin py-12 md:py-16">
      <span class="text-gold text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase">Products</span>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold font-heading mt-2 mb-4">Sharples P-3400 Decanter Centrifuge</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg max-w-2xl mb-6">The higher-capacity model in the Sharples industrial decanter series. Dolphin Centrifuge provides parts, mechanical rebuilds, and repair services for the P-3400 — a proven workhorse in wastewater, chemical, and industrial dewatering applications.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/contact-for-alfa-laval-centrifuges/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gold hover:bg-gold-light text-navy font-bold text-sm px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors">Request a Quote</a>
        <a href="tel:2485222573" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-white/30 hover:border-gold text-white font-semibold text-sm px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors">(248) 522-2573</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Specs & Content -->
  <section class="bg-warm-white">
    <div class="container-dolphin py-12 md:py-16 max-w-4xl">

      <div class="bg-navy/5 border-l-4 border-gold rounded-r-lg p-4 mb-6">
        <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed italic">Dolphin Centrifuge provides parts, mechanical rebuilds, and complete repair services for the Sharples P-3400 high-capacity horizontal decanter centrifuge — now part of the Alfa Laval portfolio. The P-3400 offers greater bowl volume than the P-3000 for higher-throughput wastewater, chemical, and industrial sludge dewatering applications. Based in Warren, Michigan, Dolphin Centrifuge has over 40 years of decanter centrifuge rebuild experience.</p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">About the Sharples P-3400</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light mb-4">
        The Sharples P-3400 is the larger-capacity model in the Sharples industrial horizontal <a href="/decanter-centrifuge/" class="text-navy font-semibold hover:text-gold transition-colors">decanter centrifuge</a> series, offering greater throughput than the <a href="/sharples-p-3000-decanter/" class="text-navy font-semibold hover:text-gold transition-colors">P-3000</a> while sharing the same proven platform architecture. The P-3400 is suited to higher-volume wastewater treatment plants, larger industrial process streams, and applications where the P-3000's capacity falls short of requirements.
      </p>
      <p class="text-text-light mb-8">
        As with the P-3000, the Sharples brand is now part of Alfa Laval, and the P-3400 is supported within the Alfa Laval service network. Dolphin Centrifuge maintains parts inventory and technical expertise for the P-3400 platform, providing rebuild and repair services to plants across North America that continue to operate these machines.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">P-3400 Specifications</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
        <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <tbody>
            <tr class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-navy">Centrifuge Model</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-text-light">Sharples P-3400</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-navy">Centrifuge Type</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-text-light">Horizontal Decanter, Two-Phase</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-navy">Capacity vs. P-3000</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-text-light">Higher (larger bowl volume)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-navy">Separation Configuration</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-text-light">Liquid-Solid (Two-Phase)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-navy">Current Brand Ownership</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-text-light">Alfa Laval (acquired)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-navy">Service Support</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-text-light">Parts, Rebuild &amp; Repair — Dolphin Centrifuge</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-white">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-navy">Typical Applications</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-text-light">Wastewater, Chemical, Industrial Sludge</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Applications</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light mb-4">The P-3400 handles the same <a href="/decanter-centrifuge-applications/" class="text-navy font-semibold hover:text-gold transition-colors">decanter centrifuge application</a> range as the P-3000, but at higher throughput:</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-2 mb-8">
        <ul class="text-text-light space-y-2">
          <li>&#8226; <a href="/wastewater-centrifuge/" class="text-navy font-semibold hover:text-gold transition-colors">Municipal wastewater sludge dewatering</a></li>
          <li>&#8226; Large-volume industrial effluent treatment</li>
          <li>&#8226; Chemical process sludge separation</li>
          <li>&#8226; Biological sludge thickening</li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="text-text-light space-y-2">
          <li>&#8226; Food processing waste dewatering</li>
          <li>&#8226; Mining and mineral slurry processing</li>
          <li>&#8226; Paper and pulp mill sludge</li>
          <li>&#8226; Rendering and industrial by-products</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">P-3400 vs. P-3000: When to Choose the Larger Model</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light mb-4">
        The P-3400 is the logical choice over the <a href="/sharples-p-3000-decanter/" class="text-navy font-semibold hover:text-gold transition-colors">P-3000</a> when plant throughput requirements exceed the smaller model's capacity. Higher daily sludge volumes, larger process flows, or the desire to operate a single larger unit instead of two smaller ones are the common drivers. Both models share the same Sharples design philosophy and are fully supported by Dolphin Centrifuge.
      </p>
      <p class="text-text-light mb-4">
        For plants evaluating whether to rebuild an existing P-3400 or upgrade to a current-generation decanter, our team can provide a comparative analysis of rebuild cost versus replacement value, spare parts availability, and performance expectations. Explore current-generation <a href="/alfa-laval-centrifuges/" class="text-navy font-semibold hover:text-gold transition-colors">Alfa Laval centrifuges</a> as upgrade options. If you need a temporary unit during rebuilding, ask about our <a href="/decanter-centrifuge-rental/" class="text-navy font-semibold hover:text-gold transition-colors">decanter centrifuge rental</a> program.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Dolphin Centrifuge P-3400 Rebuild Service</h2>
      <ul class="text-text-light space-y-2 mb-8">
        <li>&#8226; Complete bowl and scroll assembly inspection and reconditioning</li>
        <li>&#8226; Bearing replacement and precision alignment</li>
        <li>&#8226; Scroll wear surface hard-facing and replacement</li>
        <li>&#8226; Gearbox inspection and rebuild</li>
        <li>&#8226; Seal replacement and liquid end reconditioning</li>
        <li>&#8226; <a href="/industrial-disc-centrifuge-repair/" class="text-navy font-semibold hover:text-gold transition-colors">Full centrifuge repair and refurbishment services</a></li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Bottom CTA -->
      <div class="bg-navy rounded-xl p-8 text-center mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">P-3400 Parts, Rebuild or Replacement?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 max-w-lg mx-auto">Contact our team for parts availability, rebuild quotes, and upgrade path recommendations for the Sharples P-3400.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
          <a href="/contact-for-alfa-laval-centrifuges/" class="bg-gold hover:bg-gold-light text-navy font-bold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors">Get a Quote</a>
          <a href="tel:2485222573" class="border border-white/30 hover:border-gold text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors">(248) 522-2573</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
